    CougarLoggingFactory

    public class MockLoggingFactory
extends Object
implements CougarLoggingFactory
    This class provides a mock factory for testing log implementations. It must be wired in by setting the following System parameter cougar.log.factory = alternatively, add a classpath resource called CougarLoggingFactoryFQCN.txt which points to this class
